Don't stop me.

20
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:19,920
You're not allowed to go.

21
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,719
Jingqiu.

22
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:22,040
I heard on the radio

23
00:01:23,799 --> 00:01:24,599
What did it say?

24
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,400
It said

25
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,680
