Are you okay?

32
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,680
I'm fine.

33
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:44,680
The doctor saw that I looked a bit tired

34
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,520
and suggested that I

35
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,479
stay in the hospital here

36
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:47,360
and rest for a couple of days.

37
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,000
How did you get this injury?

38
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,400
It's nothing.

39
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,039
It's just that

40
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,360
when we were moving camp

41
