42
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,000
It's no big deal.

43
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:04,199
So careless.

44
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,800
But when my teammates run into trouble

45
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,400
I can't just

46
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,479
run away at the last minute, can I?

47
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:13,919
We still haven't

48
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:15,199
walked around the county town together.

49
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:15,960
Come on,

50
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:16,759
