51
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:19,919
Thank you.

52
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:20,719
Take care.

53
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:38,919
Hello.

54
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,360
Can I take a look at this fabric?

55
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,360
Of course.

56
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,479
Thank you.

57
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:50,599
It's really pretty.

58
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,599
When the hawthorn tree blooms,

59
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:55,120
it's about this color.

60
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,199
How much is this?

61
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,879
This is thirty cents per foot.

62
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,840
How much do you want?

63
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:09,759
Can you measure it for her?

64
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,439
Sure.

65
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,680
Are you

66
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:21,319
hoping to see me in new clothes?

67
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,000
Yeah.

68
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:25,079
The hawthorn trees are blooming.

69
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:26,639
I'll wear my new clothes.

70
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:27,600
Let's go see them together.

71
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,360
Is that okay?

72
00:04:28,959 --> 00:04:29,600
Sure.

73
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,800
We're almost at the station.

74
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,279
Jingqiu.

75
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:42,000
I promised your mom.

76
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,240
Now,

77
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,519
we've each broken the rules once.

78
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:45,720
So we're even.

79
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:47,399
No more next time.

80
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:52,879
You don't need to see me off.

81
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,680
Go back quickly.

82
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,399
Take care of your health.

83
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,120
It's fine.

84
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:59,000
I'll walk you.

85
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:00,279
Really, you don't have to.

86
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:19,680
Be careful.

87
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:52,639
Jingqiu

88
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:57,920
I

89
